issue.title: What use are roles?
issue.body:
Hi, i've setup my auth env variable and assigned a few roles. The docs say

```
Hubot has first class support for specify roles which a user must have to run specific commands. If you wish you use this support you must set the the following environment variables:
```

However there is on how to protect commands with these roles.

issue.title: Fixes many bugs in One Four Twentyfour game
issue.body:
The script `one_four_twentyfour.coffee` had several bugs. Including a
circular reference in `robot.brain`.

I cleaned up the code and DRY'd the saving of data to `robot.brain`.
Fixed a few edge case bugs and lowered the channel spam quotient.

comment.body: Digging this -- it looks good, but I might not be in a position to spin it up and try it for a bit...
